LINHA-DE-PESQUISA.OBJETIVOS-LINHA-DE-PESQUISA:
- mudanas climticas e doenas de plantas;
- controle fsico de doenas de plantas; 
- controle biolgico de doenas de plantas;
- solarizao do solo;
- supressividade de solos a fitopatgenos;

INFORMACOES-ADICIONAIS.DESCRICAO-INFORMACOES-ADICIONAIS-INGLES:
The book describes: 
- methodological approach to discuss impacts of climatic change on plant disease;
- Future climatic scenarios of Brazil;
- Potential impact of climate change on diseases of potato, tomato, sweet pepper, water melon, rice, winter grain, corn, soybean, banana, sugar cane, coffee, citrus, rubber, eucalyptus, incidence of nematodes, biological and chemical control of diseases in Brazil.
